CustomField.description: This field is optional. If true, the beneficiary is making a new election of payment. In the case of a formally established beneficiary IRA, it is the owner making a new election of payment.
CustomField.inlineHelpText: If true the beneficiary is making a new election of payment. In the case of a formally established beneficiary IRA it is the owner making a new election of payment.
CustomField.label: New Election of Payment Indicator
